# Concepts

Canonical vocabulary for Pi Tools.

## Project

Pi Tools is the current project context for this repository.

## Brain

The project-local knowledge graph under `.brain/`. Brain pages are authored as `.svx` and rendered by pi-notes.

## Brain Data

Large or structured source material under `.brain/data/**`. Keep raw dumps out of `.svx` pages.

## Brain Component

A reusable Svelte renderer under `.brain/components/**/*.svelte` for MDSvX notes and review surfaces.

## Review Batch

A structured browser feedback payload that should be handled with a receipt.
